name: LakeNormanWaterTemperature
0:
”Alexa ask Lake Norman the temperature”
”Alexa ask Lake Norman what is the water temperature”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: lake norman
des: This skill allows you to ask Alexa to retrieve the current water temperature of Lake Norman. The temperature is updated every 15 minutes and is retrieved from the lake in Mooresville, NC.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
